                 Electro, Dirty, Progressive | Spinnin' Records

               320 kbps | MP3 | unmixed | 2014 | 00:21:38 | 50 Mb


A hit record like 'Flute' screams for some awesome remixes! And you're in luck, we have some bangers right here! First up is the pumping Mightyfools remix. In true Mightyfools fashion it screams at you with gritty synth lines, thick basses and jump happy mini breaks. Next in line is one for you Trap lovers. The Tomsize & Simeon Festival Trap Remix brings you all the best of Flute with some grinding Trap beats to boot. Amazing!
